==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Analogically
<hw>An`a*log"ic*al*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an analogical sense;
in accordance with analogy; by way of similitude.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A prince is <qex>analogically</qex> styled a pilot, being to the
state as a pilot is to the vessel.</q> <rj><qau>Berkeley.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Analogicalness</ent>⟦br⟧
